        Secondary transformation stages.

        The purpose of this work is to minimise the modules in Primary
        to enable the OpenAccess module to complete ASAP. OA is then 
        made available to the field while the Secondary module runs.

      It is called as follows:

      exec msip_DataWhsePrimaryTransformationPart2 'Openwork', 'PrimaryTransformationPart1', 'FULL'
        or
      exec msip_DataWhsePrimaryTransformationPart2 'Openwork', 'PrimaryTransformationPart1', 'MOVE'
      
                  
