     Description:     This proc has been introduced to co-exist with the new
      proc msp_ImportTablesDropIndexes to add any indexes
      that the aforementioned proc has dropped.  Indexes are
      dropped before the BCP of the Swift tables then 
      re-created afterwards to make the BCP perform faster.

        This stored proc is called as follows:

          exec msp_ImportTablesAddIndexes 'Openwork', 'Swift'
          
        
